    "description": "<p>   STONE ZONE PTE. LTD.</p>  <p>   Position: Admin Manager            </p>  <p>   Duty:-</p>  <p>   • Provide clerical and administrative support to the department</p>  <p>   • Handle shipping documents, reports and invoices.</p>  <p>   • Data entry and maintain the filing system of the department.</p>  <p>   • Assist in sorting, organizing, and updating sales data of the internal database.</p>  <p>    </p>  <p>   Requirement:-</p>  <p>   1.       1-2 years of relevant working experience in construction industry.</p>  <p>   2.       Good communication and interpersonal skill.</p>  <p>   3.       Detail-minded, sensitive to number and figures, well organized, responsible, self motivated and willing to learn.</p>  <p>   4.       Bilingual can speak Chinese and English.</p>  <p>   5.       Immediate availability is an advantage.</p>  <p>    </p>  <p>   <strong>Email address: stonezone1101@yahoo.com.sg</strong></p>  <p>    </p>  ",
